    <ThingDef ParentName="BaseHumanMakeableGun">
        <defName>Graeme_Gun_PhasedPulseRifle</defName>
        <label>pulse rifle</label>
        <description>A charged-shot assault rifle. Phased Pulse weaponry is essentially a more refined form of the more common charged particle technology, with greatly increased accuracy.</description>
